BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:bTLcOcgesIbK1QvbaY33i
SUMMARY:Hill Talk: Stoup Brewing Capitol Hill
DTSTAMP:20260408T030253Z
DTSTART:20260414T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description    HillTalk at Stoup Brewing \\(Capitol Hill\\) Tue
	sday\, April 14  4:00-6:00 PM Join GSBA for our next HillTalk as we gathe
	r at Stoup Brewing's Capitol Hill taproom for a candid conversation about 
	what's happening in our neighborhood and what it means for local businesse
	s. HillTalk brings together GSBA members\, business owners\, community par
	tners\, and neighborhood leaders for real dialogue and practical updates. 
	Whether you're navigating public safety concerns\, city policy changes\, f
	oot traffic shifts\, or new opportunities for collaboration\, this is your
	 space to stay informed and connected. Location: Stoup Brewing - Capitol H
	ill What is HillTalk? HillTalk is a casual\, community-centered gathering 
	where Capitol Hill businesses and community members can hear timely update
	s\, ask questions\, share perspective\, and connect with the people shapin
	g our neighborhood. What to Expect Neighborhood updates impacting Capitol 
	Hill businesses Connection with fellow business owners and community partn
	ers A welcoming\, relaxed setting to build relationships and stay engaged 
	Come As You Are Grab a pint\, pull up a chair\, and be part of the convers
	ation shaping Capitol Hill's future.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/event
	s/#/details/hill-talk-stoup-brewing-capitol-hill/18425347/2026-04-14T00\n\
	nFrom SEAtoday - Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/hill-talk-stoup-brewing-c
	apitol-hill/18425347/2026-04-14T00
LOCATION:Stoup Brewing\, 1158 Broadway\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-food
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Food & Drink
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
